T1  - Gauging the efficiency of bank consolidation during a merger wave
AU  - Calomiris, Charles W.
JO  - Journal of Banking & Finance
VL  - 23
IS  - 2
SP  - 615
EP  - 621
PY  - 1999
DA  - 1999/02/01/
SN  - 0378-4266
